&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;WeightWatchers is a global digital health company.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WeightWatchers is a global digital health company and the world’s #1 doctor-recommended, clinically studied behavioral weight health program. For sixty years, we have led the industry by blending science and community to help millions of people build sustainable healthy habits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the science of weight health rapidly evolves, so does WeightWatchers. We are redefining the category by developing &lt;strong&gt;new clinical pathways for GLP-1 medication access&lt;/strong&gt;, creating specialized behavioral programs for members on weight-loss medications, and integrating medical care with our proven habit-change framework. By combining these clinical breakthroughs with our digital-first community, we are uniquely positioned to lead the future of weight health care.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Global Brand Creative Team at Weight Watchers (WW) brings our brand to life through inspiring, boundary-pushing design. We aren’t just designers; we are storytellers and problem solvers. We transform complex health journeys into powerful visuals that empower people to live healthier, longer lives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an &lt;strong&gt;Art Director&lt;/strong&gt; to serve as a key individual contributor within our in-house creative team. In this role, you are the visual architect of the &quot;360° experience.&quot; You will be responsible for ensuring our brand translates seamlessly across every possible dimension—from high-impact digital campaigns and social storytelling to tangible print and immersive physical spaces. You aren&#39;t just making assets; you are building a cohesive world for our members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;360° Brand Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the visual design for holistic brand campaigns, ensuring a unified &quot;thread&quot; connects OOH, digital media, experiential activations, and product launches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Digital &amp;amp; Social Innovation:&lt;/strong&gt; Create high-performing, mobile-first assets for web, email, and social. You have a keen eye for motion (GIFs/video) and how to stop the scroll.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Physical &amp;amp; Environmental Design:&lt;/strong&gt; Bring the brand into the real world through experiential design, brand activations, and physical environments. You understand how users interact with 3D spaces and tactile formats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative Orchestration:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the vision-lead when collaborating with specialists (photographers, illustrators, motion designers). You can direct a shoot, guide an illustrator, or use AI to create high-fidelity comps that align the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Print Mastery:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain a high standard for print excellence, overseeing everything from direct mail to large-scale OOH, with a deep understanding of production best practices (bleeds, color profiles, and substrates).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Style Guide Evolution:&lt;/strong&gt; Push the boundaries of our global style guide to create sub-branded campaign identities that feel fresh and culturally relevant while staying &quot;on brand.&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Holistic Thinker:&lt;/strong&gt; You see the big picture. You understand how a tiny social icon and a massive billboard work together to tell a single story.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expert Individual Contributor:&lt;/strong&gt; You lov

