&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity to have broad exposure across the full tax function at a growing tech health company — and to help shape the infrastructure and processes that will scale with us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
