&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for someone who enjoys solving problems, improving processes, and being the connective tissue between People strategy and day-to-day execution and who is ready to grow. We&#39;re actively building AI tooling to streamline the operational side of this work, and as that overhead reduces, the strategic scope of this role will expand (potentially to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Marketing, or Finance Organizational support).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reports to: HR Director, Business Partner Team | Hybrid, New York, NY (Chelsea) (2–3 days/week in office preferred) | No travel required.&lt;/p&gt;
