&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Business Partnership — Commercial (Sales) &amp;amp; Finance Teams (~50%)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the dedicated People Partner to a Commercial (Sales) team &amp;amp; Finance team (*about 80 employees total)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working directly with the Chief Commercial Officer and Chief Financial Officer building a trusted, high-value relationship with leadership and the team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide full-spectrum People Partner support: workforce planning, organizational effectiveness, performance management, compensation guidance, and employee relations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach managers on performance conversations, team dynamics, and leading through change the team is small enough that your impact is immediate and visible • Connect with leadership to People Team COEs (Talent Acquisition, Total Rewards, L&amp;amp;D, People Ops) and ensure programs land in a way that actually works for this team • Use people data to surface insights on team health, retention, and performance and bring those proactively to leadership rather than waiting to be asked&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational People Partner — Clinical Operations &amp;amp; Customer Support (~50%)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;WeightWatchers is a global digital health company.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WeightWatchers is a global digital health company and the world’s #1 doctor-recommended, clinically studied behavioral weight health program. For sixty years, we have led the industry by blending science and community to help millions of people build sustainable healthy habits.&lt;/p&gt;
